      <div class="fq-a">Telegrafbukta is at the southern tip of Tromsøya island, approximately 2.5 km from the city centre. Bus number 33 stops directly at Telegrafbukta. Bus number 40 stops at Tromsø Museum, approximately 300 m away. The beach is also reachable on foot or by bike along the coastal path from the city in 25–35 minutes.</div>
